      <title>重油短缺意味著托運人和道路建設者的成本更高</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/heavy-oil-shortage-spells-higher-cost-shippers-road-builders-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥的出口削減和加拿大產量的調整正在減少大西洋盆地本已有限的重質原油供應，並推高煉油廠的成本，可能對航運、建築和中東發電廠等行業產生連鎖反應。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/heavy-oil-shortage-spells-higher-cost-shippers-road-builders-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 06:04:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
