      <title>獨家：Uniper休眠的俄羅斯天然氣合約可能對上市構成障礙</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/unipers-dormant-russian-gas-contracts-may-pose-hurdle-listing-2024-05-03/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三名知情人士表示，歐洲能源危機最大的企業受害者 Uniper 正在尋求法院解決其休眠的俄羅斯天然氣供應合約問題，一旦該公司完全重返股市，該合約可能會讓投資者望而卻步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/unipers-dormant-russian-gas-contracts-may-pose-hurdle-listing-2024-05-03/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 05:05:10 GMT</pubDate>
